<aside class="span6 offset1">
  
  <p>Hacker and an occasional adventurer. Author of <a href="http://createjs.org/">Create.js</a> and <a href="http://noflojs.org/">NoFlo</a>. Decoupling software, one piece at a time. This blog tells the story of that.</p>

  
